name: FCustomFastArraySerializer
comment: Base struct for wrapping the array used in Custom Fast TArray Replication

methods.name: MarkItemDirty
methods.comment: This must be called if you add or change an item in the array

methods.name: MarkArrayDirty
methods.comment: This must be called if you just remove something from the array

methods.name: ShouldWriteFastArrayItem
methods.comment:
Helper function for FastArrayDeltaSerialize to consolidate the logic of whether to consider writing an item in a fast TArray during network serialization.
For client replay recording, we don't want to write any items that have been added to the array predictively.

properties.name: GuidReferencesMap

properties.name: CachedNumItems
properties.comment: Cached item counts, used for fast sanity checking when writing.
